OL,3,CHastings MP calls for bio-bead ban
OL,4,Cwhile Eastbourne clean-up continues
OL,6,FThe MP for Hastings and Rye, Helena
OL,7,FDollimore, has launched a campaign
OL,8,Fwith Sussex Wildlife Trust to call for
OL,9,Fan end to the use of plastic beads in
OL,10,Fwastewater treatment.
OL,12,FIt follows a major pollution incident
OL,13,Fin which millions of bio-beads were
OL,14,Freleased from Southern Water's
OL,15,FEastbourne Wastewater Treatment Plant
OL,16,Fof which the water firm has apologised
OL,17,Fand said it will pay for the clean-up.
