OL,3,CHastings MP calls for bio-bead ban
OL,4,Cwhile Eastbourne clean-up continues
OL,6,FThey washed up on Camber Sands, Rye
OL,7,FHarbour Nature Reserve and all along
OL,8,Fthe South coast. The plastic beads are
OL,9,Fharmful if swallowed by birds, fish
OL,10,Fand marine mammals who mistake them
OL,11,Ffor food.`
OL,13,FIt comes as exclusive footage given to
OL,14,FITV News Meridian from Southern Water,
OL,15,Fshows engineers investigating the tank
OL,16,Fwhere the bio beads came from,
OL,17,Fcleaning the tank and then being
OL,18,Fremoved.
