OL,6,FThe company said a filter failed
OL,7,Fduring heavy rain, allowing the beads,
OL,8,Fwhich are used in the water treatment
OL,9,Fprocess, to enter the sea.
OL,11,FDollimore recently brought Water
OL,12,FMinister Emma Hardy MP to Camber Sands
OL,13,Fto see the extent of the damage and
OL,14,Fmeet community volunteers who were
OL,15,Fcleaning it up.
