OL,3,CHastings MP calls for bio-bead ban
OL,4,Cwhile Eastbourne clean-up continues
OL,6,F"A month ago I wasn't aware that these
OL,7,Fplastic beads were used in local
OL,8,Fwastewater plants until 320 million
OL,9,Fwashed up on our beaches and nature
OL,10,Freserve, causing an environmental
OL,11,Fcatastrophe," Dollimore said.
OL,13,FShe believes they are "outdated
OL,14,Ftechnology" and is calling for water
OL,15,Ffirms to "bin the beads."
