OL,3,CHastings MP calls for bio-bead ban
OL,4,Cwhile Eastbourne clean-up continues
OL,6,F"There is only one way to guarantee
OL,7,Fthat we never have a spill of bio-
OL,8,Fbeads again, said Henri Brocklebank.
OL,9,F"That is to stop our wastewater
OL,10,Ftreatment works from using them."
OL,12,FSouthern Water confirmed in an
OL,13,Femergency residents meeting that they
OL,14,Fwill organise for marine surveyors to
OL,15,Fassess the damage to marine life, and
OL,16,Ffund a long-term programme of nature
OL,17,Frestoration.
